<div class="scrollable-container">
<div id="chart-724fa419" data-filename="724fa419" data-uri="/web/20230216220653oe_/https://www.ons.gov.uk/economy/inflationandpriceindices/bulletins/consumerpriceinflation/january2023/724fa419" class="markdown-chart">
