</div>
<h4 class="print--hide padding-top--0 margin-top--0 font-size--h6 clear-left"><span role="text">Download this chart <span class="visuallyhidden">Figure 10: Transport made the largest downward contribution to the change in the annual CPI inflation rate</span></span></h4>
<a class="btn btn--primary print--hide js-chart-image-src" data-filename="a61fa112" href="/web/20230216220653/https://www.ons.gov.uk/chartimage?uri=/economy/inflationandpriceindices/bulletins/consumerpriceinflation/january2023/a61fa112" download="Figure 10: Transport made the largest downward contribution to the change in the annual CPI inflation rate" data-gtm-title="Figure 10: Transport made the largest downward contribution to the change in the annual CPI inflation rate" data-gtm-type="download-chart-image" aria-label="Download Figure 10: Transport made the largest downward contribution to the change in the annual CPI inflation rate as an image">Image</a>
